   <pb facs="180"/>
   <head>To the Captious Reader.</head>
   <l>MY answer's this to him that saies I wrong</l>
   <l>Our <hi>Art</hi> to make my <hi>Epigrams</hi> so long;</l>
   <l>I dare not bite, therefore to change my <hi>nature,</hi>
   </l>
   <l>I call't an <hi>Epigram</hi> which is a <hi>Satire.</hi>
   </l>
</div>
